<body>
    <h1>Conversion (NEP - Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC11)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"Conversion(NEP-Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC11)-Conversio=
nworkflow">Conversion workflow</h3>
<p>Table-26</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"0=
9cc5005-05f7-4e12-b735-8af70dc63f30" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 264.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1534.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Conversion&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>This Conversion use case manages the conversion of NEP to associate.</p>=
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<p>pre-hire and hire (termination date)</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>First Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Last Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Person Number</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment Status&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hire Date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective Start Date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Start Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Department&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Position&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Email</p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>A converted account will match with the existing user <strong>personal I=
D</strong>.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>User identity object and its past access should already be present in Sa=
ilPoint.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>System Worker Type</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should b=
e equal to =E2=80=98<strong>Non-Employed Party</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>User should be in =E2=80=98<strong>Inactive</strong>=E2=80=99 status in =
SailPoint IIQ.</p></li>
<li>
<p>The downstream application access has been removed and accounts are disa=
bled.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When following conditions are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>The Assignment Effective Start&nbsp; Date should match with the current =
date.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>System Worker Type</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should b=
e changed from =E2=80=98<strong>Non-Employed Party</strong>=E2=80=99 to =E2=
=80=98<strong>Associate</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Assignment status</strong>=E2=80=99 should be equal to =
=E2=80=98<strong>Active Payroll Eligible</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Action Name</strong>=E2=80=99 should be equal to =E2=80=
=98<strong>Rehire</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>User Inactive status is =E2=80=98<strong>False</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></l=
i>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will receive a conversion flag from the HR system.<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will receive the record with the new <strong>System=
 Worker Type</strong> from the HR system for Hire.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ status is set to =E2=80=98<strong>Active</strong>=
=E2=80=99 state and is updated with the new user updated profile data and n=
ew email address(SSO identifier) will be provisioned to Oracle HCM.</p></li=
>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will enable the associated downstream application a=
ccounts.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Provision birthright access based on new user profile.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, GSuite, ServiceNow, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EP=
M Cloud, OCI.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>User account is activated in SailPoint IdentityIQ</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint will receive the record with the new worker type from the HR s=
ystem for hire.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ status set to =E2=80=98Active=E2=80=99 state and is=
 updated with the new demographic and email information</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will enable the associated downstream applications =
and provision birthright access.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Dependency:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1013" data-layout=3D"center" data-local-id=3D"83=
d6e33e-9015-43b3-93a0-9aad14785f49" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 95.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 184.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 734.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of attributes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to send the final set of attributes ma=
pping</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required for trigger</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required in the Basic Flow</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ascension Health Alliance team to confirm the list of birthright access =
applications based on demographic data</p>
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to provide users=E2=80=99 demographic =
information and access mapping</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
